The process of creating this helped me to transcend time as I fed a campfire & photographed the energetic release of smoke and embers as spirits danced around the burning logs - capturing the motion of the flames was an awe-inspiring process and the still photos are wonderful, but, I still felt like I had to do some remixing in order to truly add my energy into the mix. This fiery portal is meant transport the viewer to a place of peace inside their mind as they stare deeply into the patterns of flames engulfing themselves & re-emerge endlessly into Infinity. ... I know this one is less complex than most of the portals but...I lost my phone recently & I lost a ton of my clips that were made to be used for lengthier & more detailed animations as well as the application I used for stringing the clips together. While I'm still looking for a new software which renders in 1080p; I wanted to share this piece of my meditation, since it brought me so much joy to create.
